The paper discusses a system for querying and analyzing a large database of scientific data, which is a common topic in the database (cs.DB), distributed computing (cs.DC), and machine learning (cs.DL) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the transfer and storage of data, which is relevant to the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the development of a web service, which is relevant to the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category.
